<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>로드의 전술서:신고내역</title>
    <link href="../sources/img/로전아이콘.svg" rel="shortcut icon" type="image/x-icon">


    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.7.2/css/all.min.css" integrity="sha512-Evv84Mr4kqVGRNSgIGL/F/aIDqQb7xQ2vcrdIwxfjThSH8CSR7PBEakCr51Ck+w+/U6swU2Im1vVX0SVk9ABhg==" crossorigin="anonymous" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" />
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-QWTKZyjpPEjISv5WaRU9OFeRpok6YctnYmDr5pNlyT2bRjXh0JMhjY6hW+ALEwIH" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.13.1/font/bootstrap-icons.min.css">
    
    <link href="../css/main.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="../css/index.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>
    
        <%- include('nav_and_banner.ejs', {page: 'login', nickname: data.nickname, notice:data.banner_notice }) %> 



    <form class="container mt-5">
        <h3 class=""><신고 내역></h3>
        <p class="color-red">지정 후 버튼 누르면 일괄 적용. 종료일은 정지 처분 시에 지정됨. 삭제 지정 후 종료일 지정 안할 시 1달 뒤로 자동 지정</p>
        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-danger mt-2 mb-2">저장하기</button>
        <table class="table w-100 table-bordered table-striped">
            <thead>
                <tr>
                    <th scope="col" rowspan="2" width="28px">id</th>
                    <th scope="col" rowspan="2" width="120px">신고자</th>
                    <th scope="col" rowspan="2">신고 이유</th>
                    <th scope="col" rowspan="2" width="120px">대상 작성자</th>
                    <th scope="col" colspan="2">대상 컨텐츠</th>
                    <th scope="col" colspan="2">신고당한 횟수</th>
                    <th scope="col" colspan="2">처분</th>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <th scope="col" width="100px">종류</th>
                    <th scope="col">내용</th>
                    <th scope="col" width="55px">작성자</th>
                    <th scope="col" width="55px">컨텐츠</th>
                    <th scope="col" width="90px">종류</th>
                    <th scope="col" width="110px">종료일</th>
                </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
                <tr class="position-relative">
                    <th scope="row">1</th>
                    <td>신고자</td>
                    <td>이유</td>
                    <td>대상 작성자</td>
                    <td>대상종류</td>
                    <td class="object" data-obid=""><a href="#"> 내용 </a></td>
                    <td>작성자 횟수</td>
                    <td>컨텐츠 횟수</td>
                    <td><input readonly name="how" style="width: 80px;" value="지정 안함">
                        <ul class="report-dropdown" style="display: none;">
                            <li>삭제만</li>
                            <li>정지만</li>
                            <li>삭제+정지</li>
                            <li>지정 안함</li>
                        </ul>
                    </td>
                    <td><input type="date" name="end_date" id=""></td>
                </tr>
                
            </tbody>
        </table>
    </form>
   


    

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-YvpcrYf0tY3lHB60NNkmXc5s9fDVZLESaAA55NDzOxhy9GkcIdslK1eN7N6jIeHz" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.7.1/jquery.min.js"></script>

    <script>

    $(document).on("click", function(e){
        if(!$(e.target).closest("input[name='how']").length>0
        && !$(e.target).closest(".report-dropdown li").length>0
        ){
            $(".report-dropdown").slideUp();
            
        }
    })
    $("input[name='how']").on("click active", function(e){
        if(this.nextElementSibling.style.display == 'none'){
            $(".report-dropdown").slideUp();
            $(this).siblings(".report-dropdown").slideToggle();
        } else{
            $(".report-dropdown").slideUp();
        }
    })

    $(".report-dropdown li").on("click active", function(e){
        $(".report-dropdown").slideUp();
        $(this).parent().siblings("input").val($(this).text())
    })
    </script>
</body>
</html>